"},{"pid":"5e6dc5a86e79cf4f671007be8c2744404aa3e2c9","tid":1830461,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"講起 葵芳果隻 究竟最後點 真係報都無報"},{"pid":"d15d7e02f7ff11ea92216e2f2596d2be3cba5d68","tid":1830461,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"根據「非暴力3.5%人口」既理論，今日比較勇武既參加者(接近2%香港人口) 可以project出非暴力抗爭人數係一定過3.5%香港人口，證明場運動已經有左滾雪球既momentum，而好明顯popo係唔會停手變乖，可見雪球只會越滾越大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好像很厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79f0b597a2446ac2d58f1acb47d38f596433e5d","tid":1830461,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6dc5a86e79cf4f671007be8c2744404aa3e2c9","tid":1830461,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"講起 葵芳果隻 究竟最後點 真係報都無報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"一係popo老作做新聞<br />\n但做得新聞冇理由唔follow-up<br />\n仆街甩腳毛果個都有做訪問話自己唔係燒親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以另一個解釋就係件事係真，但唔想軍心動搖所以冷處理"},{"pid":"d2bd8a4a21fc8dce1f70fd44839e461984fe7d01","tid":1830461,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"打爛交通燈都仲可能會令市民比車撞<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知打親幾個警察對社會有乜影響，由其警察一早已經知係高危職業，正正式式人工包埋。<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔支持,唔反對,唔出手,唔阻止,見到會唔記得"},{"pid":"0619703cabf3fb9976289f48e5dbbd6b59ba547f","tid":1830461,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed469f17d9e702f13eac99c502ef84a8357aa36","tid":1830461,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d15d7e02f7ff11ea92216e2f2596d2be3cba5d68","tid":1830461,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"根據「非暴力3.5%人口」既理論，今日比較勇武既參加者(接近2%香港人口) 可以project出非暴力抗爭人數係一定過3.5%香港人口，證明場運動已經有左滾雪球既momentum，而好明顯popo係唔會停手變乖，可見雪球只會越滾越大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好像很厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/simp/vert-fut-48720142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Fsimp%2Fvert-fut-48720142&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=33b56b6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Fsimp%2Fvert-fut-48720142&h=56c16629\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/simp/vert-fut-48720142</a><br />\n個網殘體唔好屌我<br />\n<br />\n大致係講3.5%係一個有趣既數字，如果有呢一個數字既人口持續場運動 (以和平既手段)，場運動好大機會成功。<br />\n<br />\n而最有趣既一句:<br />\n「至于&ldquo;3.5%定律&rdquo;，她表示，虽然3.5%相对只是少数，但如果有这么多人参加，很可能表示有更多的人默认赞成。」<br />\n<br />\n就好似唔係人人都可以罷到工，但好多人都係支持咁"},{"pid":"76bc81a30a1977e611548c7706b10349409e582f","tid":1830461,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68302f8d1df2b2488ae3646ceaa2810abeea3294","tid":1830461,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"192df7e67da677a29e5b9eacf67f6f485972a6ab","tid":1830461,"uid":295124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"1個人出通常背後都有10個人支持 認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"我舉旺角做例子<br />\n<br />\n出黎抗爭既可能一個，但周圍行街食飯既市民街坊根本全部都係黃，好似依家咁，成班人企曬響馬路邊，一有事就企出黎。<br />\n<br />\n依家係近乎全民抗爭，只係唔係每一秒都係gear mode"},{"pid":"4dd4e30ba5c4c85919b5bdde59160259838e40f8","tid":1830461,"uid":223198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse